16:43.974 --> 16:45.975
I'm sure you'll pass with flying colors.

16:46.009 --> 16:47.977
And you have a birthday coming up too.

16:48.011 --> 16:50.946
Yes, we're gonna have a party at the house,

16:50.981 --> 16:52.982
so I'd love for you all to come.

16:53.016 --> 16:55.718
Of course. We'd love to. We'll be there.

16:58.755 --> 17:00.789
Sophia, you need to eat something.

17:00.824 --> 17:01.957
And I will.

17:04.094 --> 17:06.595
So, Dad,

17:06.630 --> 17:08.931
I have something for you.

17:08.964 --> 17:11.534
It's no big deal.

17:11.568 --> 17:13.002
Uh, yes, it is.

17:13.036 --> 17:15.604
Yeah, it's a huge deal. (Chuckles)

17:18.942 --> 17:20.876
Oh, wow.

17:24.481 --> 17:26.615
- You took this?
- You don't have to hang it up or anything.

17:26.650 --> 17:28.450
