17:28.484 --> 17:30.452
It's beautiful. Look.

17:30.487 --> 17:32.454
Oh my gosh, Callie, it's amazing.

17:32.489 --> 17:33.856
Wow, you're very talented.

17:33.890 --> 17:36.559
