have me to worry about anymore.

17:56.246 --> 17:57.446
What does that mean?

17:57.480 --> 18:01.450
When I get better, of course.

18:05.355 --> 18:07.289
He doesn't have a record, you know.

18:07.324 --> 18:08.557
